                                Kiri-Torin, friend and compatriot
  The enchantment of items is an exacting process, my friend. It is good 
that you are interested in such an undertaking, but you have no idea what 
you are getting yourself in to. 
  First off, the item has to be made of the best material to be found. Since 
the project you are describing is a weapon of power, you must use the 
best metal for a weapon. My advice would be either Adamantite or 
Mithril. These two metals both have the qualities endearing to a blade 
and both are precious enough to be of aid in the enchantment process.
  Second, the enchantment process requires a rare item that has the 
inherent magical properties you are looking for. In this case the tooth of
either a Red Dragon or a Pyrolisk would be advised. Not any tooth will 
do, therefore I suggest the Canine tooth of an elder of one of the two 
species in question.  (continues on page 2)
